data.description: Stunning, move-in ready single-story home in Northridge subdivision. Situated on a spacious lot and so many possibilities with this floorplan! Separate accessory unit with 216 sq ft could be gym, office, workshop-studio. Open living area with vaulted ceiling and fireplace. Bonus room off of kitchen provides more flex space for a little tv room-sunroom. Beautifully appointed updates throughout. Roof replaced in 2022. So many parking options with a circular drive and additional parking past gate for truck-rv-boat. This property is conveniently located to EVERYTHING! Just minutes from North Lakes Park and Recreation Center, Rayzor Ranch, Schools, universities and Goldfield Tennis Center. Stainless refrigerator conveys with home.
